				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">An the same note i also found a work around if anyonw else hasn't done it..  if your not able to locate that line to edit then search for:
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">template-&gt;assign_vars(array(
